{"tid":1181240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中] #antielab、資源分享、整合、街站","createTime":"2019-06-01T12:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:39:22.000Z","uid":140021,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"444cfe4aaa253bf45d9ce0b85a96293e170c20b0","tid":1181240,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"而家出面其實有好多資源，不過無一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平台</span></span></strong>俾人易啲搵，所以我希望可以幫手整合下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Kb2qqu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Kb2qqu.png&h=773d70f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSharing Platform: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LHChwDRhf8xrodLO7ySRlIa56CyeMI0G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1LHChwDRhf8xrodLO7ySRlIa56CyeMI0G&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e5b68236\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LHChwDRhf8xrodLO7ySRlIa56CyeMI0G</a><br />\nFlyer / IG Material: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1g66UgNOI5eDNDgowW0T4YTXEu-XaIT17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1g66UgNOI5eDNDgowW0T4YTXEu-XaIT17&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=96f627ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1g66UgNOI5eDNDgowW0T4YTXEu-XaIT17</a><br />\nProtest Material: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1b9AAzQxXiznKcAIKPz8OkTu96Wpn7Enc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1b9AAzQxXiznKcAIKPz8OkTu96Wpn7Enc&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=7e9afc7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1b9AAzQxXiznKcAIKPz8OkTu96Wpn7Enc</a><br />\nWhite House QR Code: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1BArXRd1dJ4Z__1yZkjwy3GpmqG033KJe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1BArXRd1dJ4Z__1yZkjwy3GpmqG033KJe&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=65efc701\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1BArXRd1dJ4Z__1yZkjwy3GpmqG033KJe</a><br />\nIcon / Banner: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Wzt6JknG5FVHDY9Ro2uWhu9KKtDAq94M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1Wzt6JknG5FVHDY9Ro2uWhu9KKtDAq94M&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=9a5a83c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Wzt6JknG5FVHDY9Ro2uWhu9KKtDAq94M</a><br />\n<br />\n上面有幾條link，link入面嘅file 可以俾人隨便download嚟用，主要有:<br />\n<strong>1)傳單 &amp; 資訊圖</strong><br />\n主要俾人印嚟派，或者放上social media 分享<br />\n<strong>2)profile pic &amp; banner</strong><br />\n希望同以往嘅宣傳一樣，喺social media換icon ，可以再進一步炒熱氣氛<br />\n<strong>3)遊行物資</strong><br />\n我就咁睇好似無咩人有share，雖然我有見過人自己整。用意係等啲人可以自己print 出嚟，到時遊行就咁攞住又得，痴喺紙皮上舉都得，得咗！<br />\n<br />\n現有嘅圖都係喺lihkg搵，其實唔多，希望大家有嘅可以upload 上嚟。至於icon因爲到而家都未有一個mainstream ，所以希望可以集中返用簡單#antielab，應該都唔使再設計。遊行物資方面設計要簡單啲大隻字/圖，希望media影到可以引起更大回響。<br />\n<br />\n關於flyer 想提出嘅係<br />\n1)如果白宮聯署係其中一個目標，應該加返個qr code 同網站喺flyer 上面<br />\n2)假設target嘅市場係啲中立嘅人，希望佢地轉軚，同年齡層係學生同師奶，其實flyer應該簡單少字啲，eye catching 啲<br />\n3)可以講多啲長遠嘅問題，雖然有啲難聽，不過香港大部分人關心嘅不外乎都係錢。燒到佢地，佢地就會反對。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>#antielab</em></span><br />\n希望大家多啲用個hashtag ，提高反送中資訊流通性。我地推緊一個campaign ，希望大家可以post 張相，hashtag #antielab 再tag三個frd。因為剛實行，所以推得比較慢。但如果每個連登仔都可以帶起一齊做，就可以influential 好多。我地都一路搵緊知名人士support，而佢地都準備緊。詳細可以睇睇我之前個post 同follow ig: antielabhk<br />\n傳送門:[反送中] #antiELABhk campaign<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1179897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1179897</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都加油，記得要目標一致，矛頭向外<br />\n#antielab #送中_送終<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1Sw3c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1Sw3c6.png&h=6b6faa1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e15df75d55e8f9abdddd215969c824d4a2eb67e8","tid":1181240,"uid":12804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3067bea7db8f65d1eac92c6e797a985eb49742eb","tid":1181240,"uid":19278,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4f058c57a7e29cc58ed807c43ac798ae4991ce","tid":1181240,"uid":140021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3067bea7db8f65d1eac92c6e797a985eb49742eb","tid":1181240,"uid":19278,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:35:08.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講，做得盡做"},{"pid":"bb8605feeae721bbf176a1b39bc6f8961645a11c","tid":1181240,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"如果有任何人想share 啲傳單之類，可以俾我，我up上drive"},{"pid":"09cbd70e941e8822087784c2b8df7831909abba2","tid":1181240,"uid":80033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0403075673a988d2d312b524b73502eed266abc0","tid":1181240,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"597539620117cc57f556b8ee8d610279efaad3de","tid":1181240,"uid":12804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b460b06af63f50d4dc22bc22e5c7f2c980faaf2","tid":1181240,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 